OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FOvernight low cloud in the
OL,6,FCentral Belt and east will clear
OL,7,Fthrough this morning. Otherwise it
OL,8,Fwill be a dry day with plenty of
OL,9,Fsunshine. Very warm, locally hot in
OL,10,Fthe west.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FThis evening will be dry with
OL,13,Fsome late sunshine. Then the rest of
OL,14,Fthe night will be dry but some low
OL,15,Fcloud possible in the east and Central
OL,16,FBelt.
OL,17,
OL,18,CThursday:FLow cloud dispersing through
OL,19,Fthe morning to leave a dry day with
OL,20,Fsome hazy sunshine. Very warm or hot.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
